[{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "This chapter shows how to embed images and videos."}]}, {"t": "Header", "c": [2, ["images", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Images"}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "A simple image element takes the following form: "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "![ALT_TEXT](FILENAME)"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": "."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "FILENAME"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " is the image filename (for details see "}, {"t": "Link", "c": [["", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "File locations"}], ["#file-locations", ""]]}, {"t": "Str", "c": "). "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "ALT_TEXT"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " is an alternate text for when the image cannot be displayed."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "The preferred image formats are PNG or JPG for raster graphics and SVG for vector graphics. By default an image is an inline element, meaning it will be displayed inside of a paragraph."}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["example-2.4.1", ["example"], [["data-number", "2.4.1"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "An inline image ![Star](star.png) in the regular text flow."]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "An inline image "}, {"t": "Image", "c": [["", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Star"}], ["02-elements/04-media/star.png", ""]]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " in the regular text flow."}]}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Bigger images should be wrapped in a "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "figure"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " element. This way they are formatted with a surrounding frame and can also receive a caption and a reference ID. The alternate text is referred automatically from the image title in this case."}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["example-2.4.2", ["example"], [["data-number", "2.4.2"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "::: {.figure}\n![The Creation of Adam by Michelangelo](adam.jpg \"The Creation of Adam\"){.img}\n:::"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["", ["figure"], []], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Image", "c": [["", ["img"], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "The Creation of Adam by Michelangelo"}], ["02-elements/04-media/adam.jpg", "fig:The Creation of Adam"]]}]}]]}]]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["example-2.4.3", ["example"], [["data-number", "2.4.3"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Images can also be used inside links."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "[![Logo TU Berlin](tu-logo.png)](https://www.tu-berlin.de/ \"Homepage TU Berlin\")"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Link", "c": [["", [], []], [{"t": "Image", "c": [["", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Logo TU Berlin"}], ["02-elements/04-media/tu-logo.png", ""]]}], ["https://www.tu-berlin.de/", "Homepage TU Berlin"]]}]}]]}, {"t": "Header", "c": [2, ["videos", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Videos"}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Videos are embedded similarly to images. The format is as follows: "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "[VIDEO_TITLE](FILENAME){.video .video-static}"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": "."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Use the "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "video-static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " class for files that are stored within the "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " folder or on a remote server. For embedding videos from YouTube, the "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "video-youtube"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " class is supported. Use browser-supported codecs and container format for optimal compatibility."}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["example-2.4.4", ["example"], [["data-number", "2.4.4"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Embed a video file simply by referencing its filename and adding a title."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "[Test video](video.mp4){.video .video-static}"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Link", "c": [["", ["video", "video-static"], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Test video"}], ["02-elements/04-media/video.mp4", ""]]}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Video elements can also reference a video file from an external server."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "[\"L'Arrivee d'un train en gare de la Ciotat, 1895\" from  Wikipedia](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/c3/L%27Arrivee_d%27un_train_en_gare_de_la_Ciotat%2C_1895.ogv){.video .video-static}"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Link", "c": [["", ["video", "video-static"], []], [{"t": "Quoted", "c": [{"t": "DoubleQuote"}, [{"t": "Str", "c": "L\u2019Arrivee d\u2019un train en gare de la Ciotat, 1895"}]]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " from Wikipedia"}], ["https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/c3/L%27Arrivee_d%27un_train_en_gare_de_la_Ciotat%2C_1895.ogv", ""]]}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "The following example embeds a video from YouTube."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "[Wir sind TU Berlin - Weitersagen](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OlH6bqv5Z-c){.video .video-youtube}"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Link", "c": [["", ["video", "video-youtube"], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Wir sind TU Berlin - Weitersagen"}], ["https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OlH6bqv5Z-c", ""]]}]}]]}, {"t": "Header", "c": [2, ["file-locations", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "File locations"}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "All static files reside in the "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " folder of the project root unless they point to external servers. File locations are relative to the "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " folder. It\u2019s possible to reference files from arbitrary subfolders. E.g. "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "/subfolder/math.jpg"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " refers to the file "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static/subfolder/math.jpg"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": "."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "A path specified without a leading slash is considered relative to the "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " folder plus the section path for easy file management, e.g.\u00a0"}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "tu-logo.png"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " refers to the image file "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static/02-elements/06-media/tu-logo.png"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " while "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "/tu-logo.png"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " refers to "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static/tu-logo.png"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": "."}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["example-2.4.5", ["example"], [["data-number", "2.4.5"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "An image stored in a sub-folder of "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": "."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "::: {.figure}\n![Loaded from a subfolder](/subfolder/math.jpg \"Example subfolder\"){.img}\n:::"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["", ["figure"], []], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Image", "c": [["", ["img"], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Loaded from a subfolder"}], ["subfolder/math.jpg", "fig:Example subfolder"]]}]}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "An image stored in "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static/02-elements/06-media"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": "."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "::: {.figure}\n![Logo TU Berlin](tu-logo.png)\n:::"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["", ["figure"], []], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Image", "c": [["", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Logo TU Berlin"}], ["02-elements/04-media/tu-logo.png", "fig:"]]}]}]]}]]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["info-2.4.6", ["info"], [["data-number", "2.4.6"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "When using media from external servers, please keep in mind that these"}]}, {"t": "OrderedList", "c": [[1, {"t": "Decimal"}, {"t": "Period"}], [[{"t": "Plain", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "might go offline or change at any time without notice, and"}]}], [{"t": "Plain", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "do have privacy implications for your users."}]}]]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Therefore it\u2019s generally recommended to load media from the project\u2019s "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " folder instead of relying on external services."}]}]]}, {"t": "Header", "c": [3, ["translation-of-static-files", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Translation of static files"}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "It is possible to have different versions of a static file for different languages. innoDoc will always display the language-specific file if it is present. The translated version of the file needs to be placed in the "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "_static"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " folder of the respective language."}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["example-2.4.7", ["example"], [["data-number", "2.4.7"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "For this example there are two versions of "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "lines.png"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": ", one for each language:"}]}, {"t": "BulletList", "c": [[{"t": "Plain", "c": [{"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "de/_static/02-elements/06-media/lines.png"]}]}], [{"t": "Plain", "c": [{"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "en/_static/02-elements/06-media/lines.png"]}]}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "::: {.figure}\n![Lines](lines.png)\n:::"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["", ["figure"], []], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Image", "c": [["", [], []], [{"t": "Str", "c": "Lines"}], ["_en/02-elements/04-media/lines.png", "fig:"]]}]}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Emph", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "(Try switching the language to see the other version of the file.)"}]}]}]]}]